# CODEOWNERS — governance review gates.
#
# These take effect when the repo's branch protection has
# "Require review from Code Owners" enabled (Settings -> Branches / Rulesets).
# Scope is intentionally NARROW: only funding, licensing, and CI/governance files
# require the owner's explicit review — so routine code changes are not gated, but
# tampering with sponsor/bank details, the license, or the pipelines cannot be
# merged without @pierce-lonergan's approval.

/LICENSE                 @pierce-lonergan
/COMMERCIAL-LICENSE.md   @pierce-lonergan
/.github/                @pierce-lonergan
/.github/FUNDING.yml     @pierce-lonergan
/.github/workflows/      @pierce-lonergan
/.gitleaks.toml          @pierce-lonergan
